<a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link983559" title="Flag this answer as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=983559&amp;resource_type=CommunityAnswer&amp;return_url=%2Fquestions%2F1652135-i-would-like-to-read-this-book-but-i-am%2Fanswers%2F983559-it-mentions-this-idea">flag</a>
</div>
