<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I started with Gods and Generals, am almost done, and then going to Killer Angels. I think it should be read in order because each story leads up to t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I started with Gods and Generals, am almost done, and then going to Killer Angels. I think it should be read in order because each story leads up to the next. <a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
</span>
