<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/29923.The_Last_Full_Measure"><img alt="The Last Full Measure (The Civil War Trilogy, #3)" style="height: 75px;" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1331939776l/29923._SY75_.jpg" />
